# Task 007: Alert System and Notifications

## Description
Implement a comprehensive alert and notification system for the CBSC Strategy Management Dashboard, enabling real-time monitoring and proactive response to critical events.

## Scope

### Alert Engine
- Multi-channel notification system (browser push, email, SMS)
- Alert rule engine with configurable conditions
- Alert severity levels (Info, Warning, Critical)
- Alert acknowledgment and resolution tracking
- Alert deduplication and grouping

### Notification Channels
- Browser push notifications with custom actions
- Email alerts with HTML templates
- SMS alerts for critical notifications
- In-app notification center
- WebSocket real-time alert delivery

### Alert Configuration
- Visual alert rule builder
- Threshold-based alerting
- Rate limiting and quiet hours
- Alert escalation policies
- Custom alert templates

## Tasks

### 1. Alert Engine Core (3 days)
```typescript
// Core alert engine implementation
// - Alert rule processor
// - Severity classification
// - Deduplication logic
// - Alert state management
```

### 2. Browser Push Notifications (2 days)
```typescript
// Push notification system
// - Service worker registration
// - Permission management
// - Rich notification support
// - Click action handling
```

### 3. Email Notification Service (2 days)
```typescript
// Email alert delivery
